                            We offer same-day service throughout Caledon whenever possible, including rural areas. Bolton residents can expect same-day service for most calls when you contact us before noon. For rural properties in Palgrave, Alton, Caledon East, Mayfield, and Inglewood, response times may be slightly longer depending on technician location, but we do our best to reach you the same day. We prioritize urgent repairs and emergency calls. Call <a href="tel:437-747-6737">437-747-6737</a> before noon for the best chance of same-day service anywhere in Caledon.
